  "industry_note": "OFE (C10100, Cu ≥ 99.99%, O ≤ 0.0005 — semicon grade) vs OFHC (C10200, Cu ≥ 99.95%, O ≤ 0.001 — commercial grade) / EN CW009A or CW008A. Cold-rolled (H04): σy 300 / UTS 345. ETP (C11000) 대비 O 함량 매우 낮음 → hydrogen embrittlement 회피 + high-vacuum (UHV) outgassing 회피. 반도체 vacuum chamber, particle accelerator beampipe, RF cavity (CERN, ITER), cryogenic equipment, audio (high-end speaker wire), 전기 contact.",
